
<div align="center">

 <style>
      .print td{border-top:1px #999 solid;border-right:1px #999 solid;border-bottom:1px #999 solid;border-left:1px #999 solid;}
      .print{border-top:0px #999 solid;border-right:0px #999 solid;border-bottom:0px #999 solid;border-left:0px #999 solid;}
      .print1 td{border-top:1px #999 solid;border-right:1px #999 solid; border-bottom:0px #999 solid;border-left:0px #999 solid;}
      .print1{margin-top:3px; margin-left:3px;margin-bottom:3px; margin-right:3px;border-top:0px #999 solid;border-right:0px #999 solid; border-bottom:1px #999 solid;border-left:1px #999 solid;}
      <%if params[:print] || params[:pdf] %>
          body{background-color: #dddddd;background-image:url("/images/shuiyin.png");
          background-repeat:no-repeat;background-size:80%; }
      <% end %>
      #date{ float:right;}
      .biaoti{font-family:"Times New Roman";font-size:18px}
      .title{font-family:"Times New Roman";font-size:15px}
      .time{font-family:"Times New Roman";font-size:14px}
   </style>

   <div style="width:100%" align="center"> 
      <div align="center" class="biaoti" >
          <h3>
            笔试成绩
          </h3>
      </div>  
   </div>
   <% if @written_score.present? %>

   <table class="print1" width="100%"  align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style ="font-size: 62.5%;" > 

      <tr>
        <td width="25%" height="30" align="center" class="title"><b>姓名</b></td>
        <td align="center" height="30" width="10%" class="title"><b>成绩</b></td>  
        <td align="center" height="30" width="10%" class="title"><b>录取分数线</b></td> 
      </tr>

      <tr>
          <td align="center" height="30" width="260" style="padding-left:5px" ><%= @student.name %></td>      
          <td align="center" height="30" width="60"><%= @written_score.score %></td>
          <td align="center" height="30" width="60"><%= @written_score.student_class_id %></td>
      </tr>

   </table>

   <%if @written_score.status == 1 %>
     <b>恭喜您通过2017年EMBA入学考试。</b>
   <%elsif @written_score.status == 2 %>
     <b>很抱歉告知您，未通过2017年EMBA入学考试。</b>
   <%else%>
     <b>
      <p align="left">亲爱的同学：</p>
      <p></p>
      <p align="left">您好！经过两个月的等待，2017级北京大学EMBA联考成绩终于正式公布，希望大家都能好运相伴，获得理想的成绩！</p>
      <p align="left">根据北大研究生院消息，北京大学EMBA联考分数线，以及总成绩中面试笔试所占权重目前都尚未公布，请您注意关注手机短信，一旦消息出来，我们会在第一时间给您发送通知。</p>
      <p></p>
      <p align="left">如有任何问题，欢迎致电北大国发院EMBA招生部</p>
      <p align="left">010-62755706/4802</p>  
     </b> 
   <% end %>

   <% else %>
    <b>目前笔试成绩暂不能查询。</b>

   <% end %>
  </div>